[
    {
        "text": "Hello, everyone.",
        "start": 0.5,
        "duration": 1.19
    },
    {
        "text": "This is Spike Lee,\nthe producer, writer,",
        "start": 1.69,
        "duration": 2.66
    },
    {
        "text": "director of 'Do\nthe Right Thing.'",
        "start": 4.35,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "This past June was the 30th\nanniversary of this film.",
        "start": 7.95,
        "duration": 4.83
    },
    {
        "text": "I know the column is called\n'Anatomy of a Scene.'",
        "start": 12.78,
        "duration": 4.76
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm renaming this.",
        "start": 17.54,
        "duration": 1.375
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm calling this\n'Anatomy of a Murder.'",
        "start": 18.915,
        "duration": 2.965
    },
    {
        "text": "The chokehold\nof Radio Raheem,",
        "start": 21.88,
        "duration": 4.34
    },
    {
        "text": "played by the late, great Bill\nNunn, my Morehouse brother--",
        "start": 26.22,
        "duration": 3.716
    },
    {
        "text": "\"(SINGING) Fight the power.",
        "start": 29.936,
        "duration": 1.544
    },
    {
        "text": "Fight the power.",
        "start": 31.48,
        "duration": 1.425
    },
    {
        "text": "We've got to--\"",
        "start": 32.905,
        "duration": 1.07
    },
    {
        "text": "--was based upon the\ndeath of Michael Stewart.",
        "start": 33.975,
        "duration": 3.745
    },
    {
        "text": "September 1983, Michael\nStewart, a graffiti artist--",
        "start": 37.72,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "he's about as big as I am.",
        "start": 41.26,
        "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
        "text": "11 New York City transit\npolice jumped on him",
        "start": 44.98,
        "duration": 5.19
    },
    {
        "text": "and strangled our\nbrother to death.",
        "start": 50.17,
        "duration": 4.53
    },
    {
        "text": "That's where I got the\nidea for the chokehold",
        "start": 54.7,
        "duration": 3.72
    },
    {
        "text": "murder of Radio Raheem.",
        "start": 58.42,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "And five years\nago, Eric Garner",
        "start": 61.48,
        "duration": 3.75
    },
    {
        "text": "died the same way\nthat Radio Raheem",
        "start": 65.23,
        "duration": 4.05
    },
    {
        "text": "did in a movie that was based\nupon the real life choke",
        "start": 69.28,
        "duration": 4.35
    },
    {
        "text": "hold of Michael Stewart.",
        "start": 73.63,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "So a lot of things\nin this film that",
        "start": 75.64,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "even though it was\nwritten 31 years ago",
        "start": 79.06,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "are still happening today.",
        "start": 81.88,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "Black and brown people are\nstill being murdered today",
        "start": 84.31,
        "duration": 5.28
    },
    {
        "text": "by police forces across the\nUnited States of America,",
        "start": 89.59,
        "duration": 4.05
    },
    {
        "text": "and the people who inflict\nthis death walk free--",
        "start": 93.64,
        "duration": 5.73
    },
    {
        "text": "don't get fired,\ndon't get suspended.",
        "start": 99.37,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "The film takes place one day,\nthe hottest day of summer,",
        "start": 101.81,
        "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
        "text": "in the People's Republic\nof Brooklyn, New York.",
        "start": 106.09,
        "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
        "text": "So tensions have risen\nall throughout the day.",
        "start": 109.19,
        "duration": 4.13
    },
    {
        "text": "And the reason why\nit looks the way",
        "start": 113.32,
        "duration": 1.65
    },
    {
        "text": "it is because the\nedict, the command,",
        "start": 114.97,
        "duration": 3.93
    },
    {
        "text": "to Ernest, the DP, Wynn\nThomas, the production",
        "start": 118.9,
        "duration": 2.67
    },
    {
        "text": "designer, Ruth Carter,\nthe costume designer--",
        "start": 121.57,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "here's what I told them.",
        "start": 124.99,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "I said, look, I\nwant people to be",
        "start": 126.19,
        "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
        "text": "sweating in an air\nconditioning theater",
        "start": 129.19,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "when they see this film.",
        "start": 132.34,
        "duration": 1.387
    },
    {
        "text": "[CRASHES]",
        "start": 133.727,
        "duration": 3.413
    },
    {
        "text": "And what we wanted\nto do is after he",
        "start": 137.14,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "destroys the boombox,\nit's quiet like the calm",
        "start": 140.68,
        "duration": 6.36
    },
    {
        "text": "before a storm.",
        "start": 147.04,
        "duration": 0.655
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody's like, what's next?",
        "start": 150.52,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody knows\nit gonna be bad.",
        "start": 151.78,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Everybody's looking around--",
        "start": 153.78,
        "duration": 2.266
    },
    {
        "text": "Radio Raheem.",
        "start": 156.046,
        "duration": 2.151
    },
    {
        "text": "I mean, that was personal.",
        "start": 158.197,
        "duration": 1.083
    },
    {
        "text": "It was like he got beat\nwith the baseball bat",
        "start": 159.28,
        "duration": 1.875
    },
    {
        "text": "because you've seen him the\nwhole film with his boombox",
        "start": 161.155,
        "duration": 3.215
    },
    {
        "text": "blasting Public Enemy's\n'Fight the Power.'",
        "start": 164.37,
        "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
        "text": "We did not have a very\ngood stunt coordinator,",
        "start": 168.93,
        "duration": 3.85
    },
    {
        "text": "and people got hurt.",
        "start": 172.78,
        "duration": 2.03
    },
    {
        "text": "Danny Aiello's son, Danny Jr.,\nwas his father's double right",
        "start": 174.81,
        "duration": 6.04
    },
    {
        "text": "here.",
        "start": 180.85,
        "duration": 0.66
    },
    {
        "text": "This film was shot on one\nblock in Bedford Stuyvesant.",
        "start": 181.51,
        "duration": 5.35
    },
    {
        "text": "That one block got renamed\n'Do the Right Thing",
        "start": 186.86,
        "duration": 3.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Way,' the only street in\nthe history of New York City",
        "start": 190.39,
        "duration": 4.83
    },
    {
        "text": "named after a movie.",
        "start": 195.22,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "[COMMOTION]",
        "start": 196.97,
        "duration": 3.332
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, we gotta show that,\nnumber one, Sal's Famous",
        "start": 203.17,
        "duration": 4.31
    },
    {
        "text": "Pizzeria, is on the\ncorner of the block",
        "start": 207.48,
        "duration": 2.71
    },
    {
        "text": "directly opposite the Korean\nfruit and vegetable stand.",
        "start": 210.19,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "So the fracas spilled out from\nSal's pizzeria to the street.",
        "start": 214.27,
        "duration": 6.6
    },
    {
        "text": "So we had to show the\nblock getting involved.",
        "start": 220.87,
        "duration": 6.552
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Fight!\"",
        "start": 227.422,
        "duration": 0.95
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Mookie!\"",
        "start": 228.372,
        "duration": 1.313
    },
    {
        "text": "We wanted to start down and crane\nup so you could see the block.",
        "start": 229.685,
        "duration": 4.113
    },
    {
        "text": "[COMMOTION]",
        "start": 233.798,
        "duration": 2.071
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Kill you!",
        "start": 235.869,
        "duration": 1.275
    },
    {
        "text": "We're gonna kill you, Sal!\"",
        "start": 237.144,
        "duration": 3.496
    },
    {
        "text": "And this becomes a brouhaha.",
        "start": 240.64,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "Ozzie, trying to\ntalk some sense--",
        "start": 245.09,
        "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
        "text": "the love hate rings\nwhich is a homage",
        "start": 248.41,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "to 'Night of the Hunter.'",
        "start": 251.14,
        "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Robert Mitchum had them\ntattooed on his fingers.",
        "start": 254.44,
        "duration": 2.339
    },
    {
        "text": "Now the cops come.",
        "start": 259.87,
        "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Now we already have seen\nthese two cops already.",
        "start": 263.17,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "That's Rick on the left--",
        "start": 265.41,
        "duration": 1.56
    },
    {
        "text": "that's Rick Aiello,\nDanny's son.",
        "start": 266.97,
        "duration": 2.767
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Break it up!",
        "start": 269.737,
        "duration": 0.542
    },
    {
        "text": "Break it up!",
        "start": 270.279,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Get off him!",
        "start": 270.779,
        "duration": 1.315
    },
    {
        "text": "Get off him!",
        "start": 272.094,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Get out of the way!\"",
        "start": 272.594,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "And Sandoval play\nthe other cop--",
        "start": 273.427,
        "duration": 1.533
    },
    {
        "text": "Miguel Sandoval.",
        "start": 274.96,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Now you know if\nthere's a fight,",
        "start": 276.56,
        "duration": 3.11
    },
    {
        "text": "who are they gonna grab?",
        "start": 279.67,
        "duration": 2.059
    },
    {
        "text": "\"You get over here!\"",
        "start": 281.729,
        "duration": 1.165
    },
    {
        "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
        "start": 282.894,
        "duration": 2.516
    },
    {
        "text": "So this is a very\nhard scene to shoot.",
        "start": 285.41,
        "duration": 7.2
    },
    {
        "text": "And for 31 years, it's\nbeen a hard scene to watch.",
        "start": 292.61,
        "duration": 6.477
    },
    {
        "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
        "start": 299.087,
        "duration": 3.696
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just take him down, man.\"",
        "start": 302.783,
        "duration": 1.789
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Goddammit, you're killing him!",
        "start": 304.572,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "You're killing him!\"",
        "start": 306.242,
        "duration": 1.033
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Give it up, asshole!",
        "start": 307.275,
        "duration": 0.875
    },
    {
        "text": "Give it up!\"",
        "start": 308.15,
        "duration": 1.105
    },
    {
        "text": "This is the Michael\nStewart chokehold.",
        "start": 309.255,
        "duration": 4.865
    },
    {
        "text": "And when that Eric Garner\nthing happened,",
        "start": 314.12,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "I put on my Instagram\nand Facebook",
        "start": 316.44,
        "duration": 4.28
    },
    {
        "text": "with my editor, Barry Brown,\nand we cut back and forth",
        "start": 320.72,
        "duration": 2.68
    },
    {
        "text": "between Radio Raheem\nand Eric Garner.",
        "start": 323.4,
        "duration": 4.81
    },
    {
        "text": "And it's the same thing.",
        "start": 328.21,
        "duration": 3.108
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Radio Raheem!\"",
        "start": 331.318,
        "duration": 1.916
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Radio Raheem!\"",
        "start": 333.234,
        "duration": 1.437
    },
    {
        "text": "\"No!\"",
        "start": 334.671,
        "duration": 0.809
    },
    {
        "text": "And then when he falls,\nwe laid the camera down",
        "start": 335.48,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "on the street so he would\nfall right into the lens.",
        "start": 338.12,
        "duration": 4.207
    }
]